caller_intent: The caller wanted to cancel a homeowners policy for Tony and William Brown, specifically requesting assistance with the cancellation process.
resolution_steps: Agent verified the caller's intent to cancel a property policy.
Agent attempted to locate the policy in the system but initially struggled to find it.
Agent directed the caller to send a cancellation request via email to 'bia service@travelers.com' (Business Insurance Assistance).
Agent confirmed the email address and instructed the caller to send the request to 'Dirk'.
knowledge_required: Email address for submitting cancellation requests
Handling customer inquiries about policy status
summary: The caller requested assistance canceling a homeowners policy. The agent struggled to locate the policy in the system but directed the caller to submit a cancellation request via email to Travelers' Business Insurance Assistance team. The call ended with the agent offering a post-call survey.
